{"tid":1474497,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"“ 特急!  ” 一日内比反對消滅廣東話意見!!","createTime":"2019-08-15T07:56:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T09:30:49.000Z","uid":284476,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1c286f1ccf07129dfdfe1cb196c73ae38ea90986","tid":1474497,"uid":284476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:56:40.000Z","msg":"當大家仲向到嘈緊逃犯條例時，林鄭已經修改緊中文科課程，唔洗聽同講廣東話了。<br />\n<br />\n16/9諮詢期就過啦，之後日拿拿聲上立法會一讀二讀三讀搞點。DQ埋d阻頭阻勢既議員。香港人你慢慢嘈逃犯條例啦，日日食催淚彈啦。<br />\n<br />\n#滅一個文化先滅佢既語言<br />\n#咁既政府管理香港，如果無左示威者，後果會係點？<br />\n#示威者既爆力係唔岩，但哩個政府真係無得救。<br />\n#你可以唔支持黃絲，但有一日香港失去核心價值時，唔好問點解。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.edb.gov.hk/tc/curriculum-development/kla/chi-edu/whats-new.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.edb.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fcurriculum-development%2Fkla%2Fchi-edu%2Fwhats-new.html&d=%2BEgMKdsH73Wj%2FuX4aBpXdr500bRp0Z5eW4%2BYbKsxGJA%3D&h=8299ccf5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.edb.gov.hk/tc/curriculum-development/kla/chi-edu/whats-new.html</a><br />\n<br />\n3. 2002 年的《中國語文教育學習領域 《中國語文教育學習領域課程指引》中指出「用普通話教中 「用普通話教中<br />\n文」為遠程目標。是次修訂，教育局有何建議 ，教育局有何建議？<br />\n現時不少學者和學校對於以普通話教授中國語文（「普教中」）仍持有不<br />\n同意見。由於「普教中」的成效受很多因素影響，包括教師運用普通話<br />\n的能力、學校的語言環境，以及學生的社交圈子等，因此，建議學校可<br />\n因應校情，包括教師的資歷、學生的水平、校園的語境、課程的編排、<br />\n教學的支援等因素，考慮是否用普通話教授中國語文，或採用何種方式用（普教中）<br />\n<br />\n16/9終止諮詢的是：[url]<strong><strong><a href=\"https://www.edb.gov.hk/attachment/tc/about-edb/press/consultation/TF_CurriculumReview_Consultation_c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.edb.gov.hk%2Fattachment%2Ftc%2Fabout-edb%2Fpress%2Fconsultation%2FTF_CurriculumReview_Consultation_c.pdf&d=%2BEgMKdsH73Wj%2FuX4aBpXdr500bRp0Z5eW4%2BYbKsxGJA%3D&h=0ed5afb3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.edb.gov.hk/attachment/tc/about-edb/press/consultation/TF_CurriculumReview_Consultation_c.pdf</a></strong></strong>[/url]"},{"pid":"b59ab7328e9da772424fbeff10d0a63d640c31e4","tid":1474497,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:57:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5e30ea884ead877d85a4c44134c5e3fd5de05b31","tid":1474497,"uid":67225,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:59:23.000Z","msg":"居然夠擔話因為係母語所以唔洗考<br />\n而家條街好多細路仔唔識講政府口中嘅母語喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96e6efc24a3e2ad6634254c92fe2b734eb6a4f88","tid":1474497,"uid":92353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T08:00:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0a0308180f9cf206ec0ee6fadedd421dcf41130e","tid":1474497,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T08:00:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>居然夠膽話因為係母語所以唔洗考<br />\n但而家條街好多細路仔都唔識講政府口中嘅母語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"a4c5ad69e1dd9098488c340877b0f86d0caa82d0","tid":1474497,"uid":92353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5e30ea884ead877d85a4c44134c5e3fd5de05b31","tid":1474497,"uid":67225,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:59:23.000Z","msg":"居然夠擔話因為係母語所以唔洗考<br />\n而家條街好多細路仔唔識講政府口中嘅母語喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T08:03:35.000Z","msg":"全中國cut曬中文科改上英文堂"},{"pid":"4b3f874cfa3ffc5f874961e3100568718956aa62","tid":1474497,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T08:04:45.000Z","msg":"守護粵語   反送終"},{"pid":"c03396c86487d431f91ff45d3a90510d8bfdab3d","tid":1474497,"uid":111955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T08:29:42.000Z","msg":"文宣一流<br />\n<br />\n中共出招消滅粵語，新殭集中營翻版"},{"pid":"ce7807def879e1c3628a3a7b2035c7cfa253feb8","tid":1474497,"uid":268073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T09:1